title: Athlete of the Week - Emilee Harris
text: Emilee Harris - Woodstock - VolleyballEmilee Harris played her best volleyball for Woodstock when it mattered the most.The sophomore outside hitter and defensive specialist recorded 78 kills with an attack percentage of .446, along with 60 digs, 10 aces and seven blocks as Woodstock has gone 4-2 over the last week and clinched a berth in the state playoffs. How long sheâ€™s played volleyball: Four years Favorite thing about the sport: The energy and meeting and becoming close with the team Favorite color: Green Favorite movie: The Blind Side Favorite musical artist: The Weeknd Dream vacation: London Favorite sports team: Atlanta Braves Plans for after college: Play professional volleyball in Europe
